    "Promueve": "Promotes the use of urban ponds as biodiversity reservoirs and stepping stones for species migration.",
    "Restablece": "Restores hydrological balance by enhancing connectivity with other water bodies and managing pollutant levels.",
    "Fomenta": "Fosters healthier freshwater habitats by improving water quality and supporting diverse aquatic ecosystems.",
    "Gobierna": "Encourages policies to prevent habitat degradation and promote sustainable urban pond management."
